    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44368</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_020_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>君たちは私のことを誰に？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Who was the one that told you about me?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44444</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_020_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Arche&gt;さんに聞きました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We heard from Miss &lt;Arche&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_020_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Arche&gt;に会ったのか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So you've met &lt;Arche&gt;...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44628</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_020_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>君たちの時代にいたということは
２００歳の彼女だな、それは</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In your era she'd be about 200 years old...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44736</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_020_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>２００歳……そんなに長く生きるって
どんな気持ちなんだろ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>200 years...I wonder how she feels after such a long time...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44828</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_020_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>人がひとりで生きるには
長すぎる時間だな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>People can easily live alone for long periods of time, uh?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44948</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_020_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、仲間がいれば、どんな長い年月だって
きっと乗り越えられる……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>When one is with a companion you can overcome any amount of time...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45040</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_020_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、ひとりは……
やっぱり寂しい……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But it's just too sad...being alone...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45100</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_020_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エト？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eto?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45208</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_020_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え？　あ、ううん……&lt;Arche&gt;さん、
どうしてひとりなんだろ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Eh? Oh it's ok. So why was &lt;Arche&gt; alone in the first place?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45340</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_020_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>一番大切な思い出が彼女の中で大きすぎる。
誰もその穴を埋められない。それどころか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>She keeps her memories very dearly inside her. She created a hole she couldn't fill.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45464</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_020_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>人といるとその時のことを思い出して
よけいに彼女を寂しくしてしまうから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>With no one to share them, each time she remembers such things she would probably go through a lot of sadness...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45536</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_020_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう、なんですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is that...really true?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45600</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_020_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……かもな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Sadly, yes...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45668</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_020_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルルル～……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kurururu...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
